        "Algerian War": "Algerian War"
    },
    {
        ".     Camus was a strong supporter of European integration and participated in various marginal organisations working towards that end. In 1944, he founded the Comité Français pour la Féderation Européenne—CFFE declaring that Europe can only evolve along the path of economic progress, democracy, and peace if the nation states become a federation.  In 1947–48, he founded the Groupes de liaison internationale—GLI , a trade union movement in the context of revolutionary ": null
