        " first introduced him at a meeting of the Cercle des Étudiants Anarchistes in 1948 as a sympathiser familiar with anarchist thought. Camus wrote for anarchist publications such as  Le Libertaire ,  La Révolution prolétarienne , and  Solidaridad Obrera  , the organ of the anarcho-syndicalist ": null
